README

    Requisites : java and maven installed and an internet connection to download dependencies

	Build

		download the task_lottoland project in some path
		cd path/task_lottoland
		mvn install

	Run

		java -jar target/task-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar

		Or if want to do a remote debug using port 8001
			java -agentlib:jdwp=transport=dt_socket,server=y,suspend=n,address=8001 -jar target/task-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar

		Or using the spring boot maven plugin from the IDE 
			mvn spring-boot:run

	Use

        http://host-name:8080/page.html

        Locally could use
            http://localhost:8080/page.html

    Rest API

		There are 2 endpoints.

		- playRound: POST  /play
            play a round and return the result

		- totalsAccumulator: GET /totals
            return the totals for all the games played



